description:
UEFA Champions League ITV Highlights 2016-04-13 HDTV 1080p 2ch x265 [S-Less]

Action from the concluding quarter-final second-leg matches, featuring Atletico Madrid v Barcelona at the Estadio Vicente Calderon and Benfica v Bayern Munich at the Estadio da Luz. Plus, a look back at Tuesday's fixtures, which were Manchester City v Paris Saint-Germain and Real Madrid v VfL Wolfsburg. Presented by Mark Pougatch, with commentary by Joe Speight and Sam Matterface, and analysis from Roy Keane and Lee Dixon
